### Listen to Authentication State Changes in JavaScript

Source: https://context7.com/supabase/supabase-js/llms.txt

Subscribes to authentication events such as sign-in, sign-out, and token refresh. Provides real-time notifications of auth state transitions. Returns subscription object for cleanup and unsubscribing.

```javascript
const { data: { subscription } } = auth.onAuthStateChange((event, session) => {
  console.log('Auth event:', event)
  if (session) {
    console.log('User ID:', session.user.id)
  }
})
```

